{"word":"G4417 - πταίω - ptaíō - ptah'-yo - Fall","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πταίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ptaíō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ptah'-yo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fall"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இடறு, தவறு, இடறிவிழு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to cause one to stumble or fall"},{"paragraph":"2. to stumble"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A form of <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>trip</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>err</i>, <i>sin</i>, <i>fail</i> (of salvation): - fall, offend, stumble."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}